{
  "texts": [
    "At each time step t,",
    "• a new object x t is revealed,",
    "• the forecaster must propose a prediction ŷt of the label of y t,",
    "• the true label y t ∈ {0, 1} is revealed and the forecaster incurs a loss ℓ(ŷ t, y t), and updates his/her knowledge.",
    "Similarly, online regression and other online prediction problems are studied."
  ]
}